src.pq

Class ArrayPriorityQueue<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.pq.ArrayPriorityQueue<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iPriorityQueue<K,V>

    public class ArrayPriorityQueue<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements iPriorityQueue<K,V>
    Priority Queue implemented using an ArrayList. Lowest Priority is found by using selection sort on removal. Elements are stored in the order they are inserted in.
    Since:
    v1.1
